{"tid":1542860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係女義士見到d冷血軍師開香檳咁款都跳樓啦","createTime":"2019-09-05T03:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T04:12:30.000Z","uid":31637,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f7e5498ed543c9c5e380f52471869daa94842bfb","tid":1542860,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"我發現對得班冷血軍師同左膠越耐，越覺得黃屍陣營冷血又冷漠<br />\n已經唔撚想投比呢班人支持既後選人<br />\n班冷血既軍師同左膠以為玉碎派趕走民意<br />\n事實剛好相反，係你班左膠同冷氣軍師趕走民意<br />\n我係玉碎派身上睇到團結，熱血，勇氣，互相守望<br />\n我係冷血軍師同左膠身上睇到自私，冷血，軟弱，民意比手足更重要<br />\n搞抗爭搞撚到開撚晒party咁，爭取到條鳩毛返黎就開撚晒香檳咁款<br />\n有人想為死去既手足報仇，就強硬阻止，輿論降溫，仲畫出腸地認為民意比手足條命更重要，要顧全大局，唔好報仇<br />\n<br />\n我決定由今日開始做中立派，唔撚再支持你班濕鳩黃屍，唔係因為玉碎派，係因為你班冷血軍師同左膠<br />\n<br />\n以前唔明點解係美國以外,比獨裁國家am緊既人民都覺得奧巴馬同班liberals偽善<br />\n今日終於明晒<br />\n你班冷血既人繼續圍爐企係自己set既道德高地啦"},{"pid":"2db206d39108ea91b9d2e3b614830bdaee92d61c","tid":1542860,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7Lwx.jpg&h=5719ebc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoyFk4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://